  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Trading electricity from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How cross-border trading and supply of electricity will be affected from 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

